OL,5,CBIKE-RAGE                   Q"d8!! "d8!
OL,6,                             R/,,////,,/
OL,7, Teletext viewerCHannah Chapman, 29,Gof 
OL,8,CEaling,Gcycles into the City of London 
OL,9,Geveryday. She says she often loses her 
OL,10, temper when cars "cut her up".         
OL,12, "I gave up my car for a bike seven     
OL,13, years ago in a bid to get fit, and as a
OL,14, way toCalleviate tension.              
OL,16, "I might have got fitter, but the      
OL,17, stress has got worse. Drivers send me  
OL,18, potty. They seem to think thatCthey own
OL,19,Cthe road,"Gshe adds.                   
