OL,5,CBIKE-RAGE                   Q"d8!! "d8!
OL,6,G                            R/,,////,,/
OL,7,GCyclist Hannah Chapman - maddened by a 
OL,8,Gmotorist whom she claims dangerously   
OL,9,Gcut her up on a side road - pulled off 
OL,10,Gthe driver'sCwindscreen wipersGin      
OL,11,Gretaliation.                           
OL,12,G                                       
OL,13,GShe says: "I know it wasn't a good idea
OL,14,Gbut I just lost it. The driver stopped 
OL,15,Ghis car, got out andCthumped me.       
OL,16,G                                       
OL,17,G"It'sCa war-zoneGout there and         
OL,18,Gpersonally, I don't know how, if ever, 
OL,19,Git can be controlled."                 
