OL,5,CBIKE-RAGE                   Q"d8!! "d8!
OL,6,                             R/,,////,,/
OL,7,CPensioner Christopher Keane,Gfrom      
OL,8,CNorfolk,Gsays traffic on Britain's     
OL,9,Groads has changed dramatically over the
OL,10,Glast 30 years.                         
OL,11,G                                       
OL,12,G"It's getting more and more likeCNew   
OL,13,CDelhi,Gwhat with all the different     
OL,14,Gmodes of transport. As for cyclists,   
OL,15,Gthey're a nuisance.                    
OL,16,G                                       
OL,17,G"They swing in and out of traffic - you
OL,18,Ccan hardly see them.GIt's dangerous,   
OL,19,Gand it's no wonder motorists lash out."
