OL,5,CBIKE-RAGE                   Q"d8!! "d8!
OL,6,                             R/,,////,,/
OL,7,CKirsten Smith, 26,GfromCNorwood Green, 
OL,8,Ghas given up her bicycle after she was 
OL,9,Gchased by a "lunatic driver".          
OL,10,G                                       
OL,11,G"At first I tried to ignore him, but   
OL,12,Gwhen we stopped at traffic lights, I   
OL,13,Gcouldn't control myself. His window was
OL,14,Gwide open andCI simply spat at him.GIt 
OL,15,Ghit him right on the nose.             
OL,16,G                                       
OL,17,G"It's all well and good telling people 
OL,18,Gto use eco-friendly modes of transport 
OL,19,Glike bikes, butCis it safe?"           
